Map<String, Long> map = Arrays.stream(str.split(" "))
        .collect(Collectors.groupingBy(
                Function.identity(),
                Collectors.counting()));

System.out.println(map);

Output

{java=3, spring=2, react=1}
3. Find Duplicate Elements
